quran[5{c,v,t}:
24,54,"kaho,"" Allah ke Mutee bano aur Rasool Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam ke tabay farmaan ban kar raho lekin agar tum mun phertey ho to khoob samajh lau ke Rasool Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam par jis farz ka baar rakha gaya hai uss ka zimma daar woh hai aur tum par jis farz ka baar dala gaya hai uss ke zimma daar tum ho uss ki itaat karo ge to khud hi hadaayat pao ge warna rasool ki zimma daari is se ziyada kuch nahi hai ke saaf saaf hukum pouncha day """
24,55,"Allah ne wada farmaya hai tum mein se unn logon ke sath jo imaan layein aur naik amal karen ke woh un ko usi terhan zameen mein khalifa banaye ga jis terhan unn se pehlay guzray hue logon ko bana chuka hai, unn ke liye unn ke uss deen ko mazboot bunyadon par qaim kar day ga jisay Allah taala ne unn ke haq mein pasand kya hai, aur unn ki ( mojooda ) haalat khauf ko aman se badal day ga, bas woh meri bandagi karen aur mere sath kisi ko shareek nah karen aur jo is ke baad kufar kere to aisay hi log fasik hain"
24,56,"namaz qaim karo, zkoh do, aur Rasool Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam ki itaat karo, umeed hai ke tum par reham kya jaye ga"
24,57,jo log kufar kar rahay hain a noon ke mutaliq is ghalat fehmi mein nah raho ke woh zameen mein Allah ko aajiz kar den ge un ka thikana dozakh hai aur woh bara hi bura thikana hai
24,58,"ae logo jo imaan laaye ho, lazim hai ke tumahray mamlook aur tumahray woh bachay jo abhi aqal ki hadd ko nahi puhanche hain, teen auqaat mein ijazat le kar tumahray paas aaya karen : subah ki namaz se pehlay, aur dopehar ko jabkay tum kapray utaar kar rakh dete ho, aur esha ki namaz ke baad yeh teen waqt tumahray liye parday ke waqt hain inn ke baad woh bulaa ijazat ayen to nah tum par koi gunah hai nah unn par, tumhe aik dosray ke paas baar baar aana hi hota hai is terhan Allah tumahray liye apne arshadat ki tozeeh karta hai, aur woh Aleem o hakeem hai"
